Package: esspenR
Type: Package
Title: Access ESPN API Data with Clean Data Frames
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Tomaro", 
           email = "daniel.tomaro@icloud.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides access to ESPN's undocumented API endpoints, returning 
    clean, structured data frames for sports data analysis. Covers multiple 
    sports including NFL, NBA, MLB, NHL, college sports, and soccer. Functions 
    extract and clean data from scoreboards, team information, player statistics, 
    standings, news, and more. Users can choose between processed data frames 
    (default) or raw JSON responses. Please note this uses unofficial APIs that 
    may change without notice.
